<h3>Stable version</h3>
<p class="intro">
Stable edition of Interchange for production environments.
</p>

<p>
The current stable release of Interchange is <strong>5.6.1</strong>. It was released 16th November 2008.
</p>

<p>
For a list of new features and fixes, you should check the <a href="#">What's New</a> list.
</p>

