<div class="oneThirdGrad">
<h3>Installation</h3>
<p class="intro">
Get your Interchange running.
</p>

<p>
Installing Interchange is about as complicated as any other server software in Linux. We have prepared <a href="#">Installation instructions</a> to help you on the way.
</p>

<p>
In case you are not that good at Linux you can get support from some of the companies that offer <a href="#">Interchange professional support</a>.
</p>

<h4>Resources:</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="[area download]">Installation instructions</a></li>
