<div class="oneThirdGrad">
<h3>Prerequisites</h3>
<p class="intro">
Things Interchange needs.
</p>

<ul>
<li>Linux or similar operating system<br>(Linux, BSD, MacOS,...).</li>
<li>Web server<br>(Apache, lighttpd, nginx,...)</li>
<li>Perl 5.8 or higher</li>
<li>Database<br>(PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLLite,...)</li>
</ul>

<p>
Most of the Linux distributions offer all packages required for Interchange to function properly.
</p>
<p>
For details on how to make them work with Interchange, check <a href="#">Installation instructions</a>.
</p>

</div>

